<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="{{ description or 'Building AI products and systems — documented by Geo Vega.' }}">
  <title>{% if title %}{{ title }} | {% endif %}Geo AI Builds</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #0f0f0f; color: #e8e2d9; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 17px; }
    a { color: #a855f7; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    header { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #222; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }
    header .logo { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #a855f7; }
    header nav a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    main { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.5rem 2rem; }
    footer { max-width: 860px; margin: 3rem auto 0; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #222; color: #555; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <a href="/" class="logo">Geo AI Builds</a>
    <nav>
      <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
      <a href="https://geo-ai-tools.netlify.app">Tools →</a>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main>{{ content | safe }}</main>
  <footer>Geo · AI Generalist &amp; Builder · <a href="https://geo-ai-tools.netlify.app">geo-ai-tools</a></footer>
</body>
</html>
